// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0087 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: a4f82031-7dc2-5b58-80e2-4cb49a6d4491

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:10*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:20.04-ESM*")
